{
  "texts": [
    "Among the models, Random Forest demonstrated the highest overall performance.",
    "It excelled in terms of accuracy, precision, and F1-score, making it a strong candidate for intrusion detection applications.",
    "These results show that machine learning models can effectively identify network anomalies, contributing to improved cybersecurity.",
    "The choice of the most suitable model depends on specific application requirements and tradeoffs between precision and recall.",
    "The model architecture consists of two LSTM layers followed by a Dense layer with a softmax activation function."
  ]
}